 mass has been deposited at the center of a halo matters, but also the\nmode of its deposition. It might prove impossible to predict the halo response\nwithout a detailed understanding of a galaxy's assembly history. (Abriged)\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sat, 14 Feb 2009 16:49:04 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-05-13"}
