ults are in an complete agreement\nwith estimations made within the continuum-limit approach.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sun, 15 Feb 2009 08:23:17 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 25 Jul 2012 07:57:29 GMT"}],"update_date":"2012-07-26"}
